Package: DSGE
Type: Package
Title: Disruption Score of Gene Expression — Pathway-Level
    Transcriptional Disruption Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("LHJLab", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "lihuijuan@xzhmu.edu.cn")
Description: Converts DESeq2 differential expression p-values into
    absolute z-scores and tests whether Gene Ontology pathways show
    significantly stronger transcriptional disruption than expected by
    chance, using permutation-based null distributions grouped by
    pathway size with Benjamini-Hochberg FDR correction.
    Includes utilities for reading GAF 2.2 annotation files and OBO
    ontology files.
